column5: Happy Birthday Joey, hope you had a great weekend.  Best regards, Sam

PARTY PARTY JOEY!!!!

happy birthday

Thanks guys, its been a great weekend so far.  Yesterday we fished all day and I caught a pike, then today I shopped all morning with my mother.  Tonight I'm having Mom over for mother's day dinner and a little birthday celebration for some steak, bacon wrapped pike and strawberry/rhubarb pie.  Then we'll watch the finale of Survivor!!  Can't bet any better than that, woohoo.  Thanks again!!!!  Cheers,  Joey
Well it could be if Tybo keeps his end of the birthday bargain up!  Have a great day Joey!
Joey, Joey, Joey; I don't know how you do it, you have birthdays and you never look any older, just more beautiful!  Hope you have a wonderful day today and all year through!  Happy Birthday kid!
Happy Birthday and enjoy what's left of the day!
A very Happy Birthday to you...you reminded me of Survivor...
